#. <section class="sutta" id="sn16.7"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn16.7:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 16"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 16"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn16.7:0.2"
msgid "1. Kassapavagga"
msgstr "1. Kassapa"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn16.7:0.3"
msgid "7. Dutiyaovādasutta"
msgstr "7. Advice (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.206"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: veḷuvane → sāvatthiyaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "sn16.7:1.1"
msgid "Rājagahe viharati veḷuvane."
msgstr "Near Rājagaha, in the Bamboo Grove."

msgctxt "sn16.7:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā mahākassapo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami … pe …"
msgstr ""
"Then Venerable Mahākassapa went up to the Buddha, bowed, and sat down to one "
"side."

msgctxt "sn16.7:1.3"
msgid "ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho āyasmantaṃ mahākassapaṃ bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr "The Buddha said to him:"

msgctxt "sn16.7:1.4"
msgid "“ovada, kassapa, bhikkhū;"
msgstr "“Kassapa, advise the mendicants!"

msgctxt "sn16.7:1.5"
msgid "karohi, kassapa, bhikkhūnaṃ dhammiṃ kathaṃ."
msgstr "Give them a Dhamma talk!"

msgctxt "sn16.7:1.6"
msgid "Ahaṃ vā, kassapa, bhikkhū ovadeyyaṃ tvaṃ vā;"
msgstr "Either you or I should advise the mendicants"

msgctxt "sn16.7:1.7"
msgid "ahaṃ vā bhikkhūnaṃ dhammiṃ kathaṃ kareyyaṃ tvaṃ vā”ti."
msgstr "and give them a Dhamma talk.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn16.7:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Dubbacā kho, bhante, etarahi bhikkhū, dovacassakaraṇehi dhammehi "
"samannāgatā akkhamā appadakkhiṇaggāhino anusāsaniṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Sir, the mendicants these days are hard to admonish, having qualities that "
"make them hard to admonish. They’re impatient, and don’t take instruction "
"respectfully."

#. VAR: hirī → hiri (sabbattha)
#. VAR: āgacchati → āgacchanti (si)
msgctxt "sn16.7:2.2"
msgid ""
"Yassa kassaci, bhante, saddhā natthi kusalesu dhammesu, hirī natthi kusalesu "
"dhammesu, ottappaṃ natthi kusalesu dhammesu, vīriyaṃ natthi kusalesu "
"dhammesu, paññā natthi kusalesu dhammesu, tassa yā ratti vā divaso vā "
"āgacchati, hāniyeva pāṭikaṅkhā kusalesu dhammesu, no vuddhi."
msgstr ""
"Sir, whoever has no faith, conscience, prudence, energy, or wisdom when it "
"comes to skillful qualities can expect decline, not growth, in skillful "
"qualities, whether by day or by night."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn16.7:3.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhante, kāḷapakkhe candassa yā ratti vā divaso vā āgacchati, "
"hāyateva vaṇṇena, hāyati maṇḍalena, hāyati ābhāya, hāyati ārohapariṇāhena."
msgstr ""
"It’s like the moon in the waning fortnight. Whether by day or by night, its "
"beauty, roundness, light, and diameter and circumference only decline."

msgctxt "sn16.7:3.2"
msgid ""
"Evameva kho, bhante, yassa kassaci saddhā natthi kusalesu dhammesu … pe …"
msgstr ""
"In the same way, whoever has no faith, conscience, prudence, energy, and "
"wisdom when it comes to skillful qualities can expect decline, not growth, "
"in skillful qualities, whether by day or by night."

msgctxt "sn16.7:3.3"
msgid "hirī natthi …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn16.7:3.4"
msgid "ottappaṃ natthi …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn16.7:3.5"
msgid "vīriyaṃ natthi …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn16.7:3.6"
msgid ""
"paññā natthi … kusalesu dhammesu tassa yā ratti vā divaso vā āgacchati, "
"hāniyeva pāṭikaṅkhā kusalesu dhammesu, no vuddhi."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn16.7:4.1"
msgid "‘Assaddho purisapuggalo’ti, bhante, parihānametaṃ;"
msgstr "A faithless individual is in decline."

msgctxt "sn16.7:4.2"
msgid "‘ahiriko purisapuggalo’ti, bhante, parihānametaṃ;"
msgstr "An individual with no conscience is in decline."

msgctxt "sn16.7:4.3"
msgid "‘anottappī purisapuggalo’ti, bhante, parihānametaṃ;"
msgstr "An imprudent individual is in decline."

msgctxt "sn16.7:4.4"
msgid "‘kusīto purisapuggalo’ti, bhante, parihānametaṃ;"
msgstr "A lazy individual is in decline."

msgctxt "sn16.7:4.5"
msgid "‘duppañño purisapuggalo’ti, bhante, parihānametaṃ;"
msgstr "A witless individual is in decline."

msgctxt "sn16.7:4.6"
msgid "‘kodhano purisapuggalo’ti, bhante, parihānametaṃ;"
msgstr "An angry individual is in decline."

msgctxt "sn16.7:4.7"
msgid "‘upanāhī purisapuggalo’ti, bhante, parihānametaṃ;"
msgstr "A hostile individual is in decline."

msgctxt "sn16.7:4.8"
msgid "‘na santi bhikkhū ovādakā’ti, bhante, parihānametaṃ."
msgstr "When there are no mendicant advisers there is decline."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn16.7:5.1"
msgid ""
"Yassa kassaci, bhante, saddhā atthi kusalesu dhammesu, hirī atthi kusalesu "
"dhammesu, ottappaṃ atthi kusalesu dhammesu, vīriyaṃ atthi kusalesu dhammesu, "
"paññā atthi kusalesu dhammesu, tassa yā ratti vā divaso vā āgacchati, "
"vuddhiyeva pāṭikaṅkhā kusalesu dhammesu, no parihāni."
msgstr ""
"Sir, whoever has faith, conscience, prudence, energy, and wisdom when it "
"comes to skillful qualities can expect growth, not decline, in skillful "
"qualities, whether by day or by night."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.207"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn16.7:6.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhante, juṇhapakkhe candassa yā ratti vā divaso vā āgacchati, "
"vaḍḍhateva vaṇṇena, vaḍḍhati maṇḍalena, vaḍḍhati ābhāya, vaḍḍhati "
"ārohapariṇāhena."
msgstr ""
"It’s like the moon in the waxing fortnight. Whether by day or by night, its "
"beauty, roundness, light, and diameter and circumference only grow."

msgctxt "sn16.7:6.2"
msgid "Evameva kho, bhante, yassa kassaci saddhā atthi kusalesu dhammesu …"
msgstr ""
"In the same way, whoever has faith, conscience, prudence, energy, and wisdom "
"when it comes to skillful qualities can expect growth, not decline, in "
"skillful qualities, whether by day or by night."

msgctxt "sn16.7:6.3"
msgid "hirī atthi … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn16.7:6.4"
msgid "ottappaṃ atthi …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn16.7:6.5"
